properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 24 at 12:19AM EST until January 24 at 5:00AM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the Dense Fog Advisory, dense fog will reduce
visibility to 1 NM or less at times. For the Small Craft
Advisory, seas 5 to 7 feet.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach
FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...For the Dense Fog Advisory, until 5 AM EST early this
morning. For the Small Craft Advisory, until 4 AM EST early
this morning.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft. Low
visibility will make navigation difficult, especially near
inlets.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 5 AM EST EARLY THIS MORNING... ...SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM EST EARLY THIS MORNING
